                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for separating titanium and iron from low-titanium vanadium titano-magnetite",
                    "一种低钛型钒钛磁铁矿的钛铁分离方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a titanium-iron separation method for low-titanium type vanadium-titanium magnetite, and belongs to the technical field of mineral processing, the low-titanium type vanadium-titanium magnetite is subjected to hydrogen selective reduction regulation treatment, so that the outer layer of iron oxide is reduced into coated metal iron, and titanium-iron oxide is not reduced; and then the obtained reduction product is subjected to magnetic separation to achieve effective separation of titanium minerals and iron minerals, and concentrate with the high iron content and tailings with the high titanium content are obtained. According to the ferrotitanium separation method, the H2 + Ar or H2 + H2O + Ar reducing atmosphere is adopted, the technical defects that pollutant emission is increased and high titanium slag is generated due to the fact that coal-based or carbon-based direct reduction treatment is adopted are overcome, the ferrotitanium separation method has the advantages of being low in carbon, environmentally friendly, low in reduction temperature, free of any additive and the like, magnetic separation products obtained after low-intensity magnetic separation can provide production raw materials for a blast furnace or an electric furnace, and the production cost is reduced. The magnetic separation tailings can provide a direction for preparing the ferrotitanium alloy, and the method is expected to be developed into a new concept technological process for zero-emission clean mineral processing and smelting in the future."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种低钛型钒钛磁铁矿的钛铁分离方法，属于矿物加工技术领域，先将低钛型钒钛磁铁矿进行氢的选择性还原调控处理，使得铁氧化物外层还原为包覆态金属铁，而钛铁氧化物不被还原，然后将得到的还原产物经过磁选以实现钛矿物和铁矿物的有效分离，得到含铁量较高的精矿和含钛量较高的尾矿。本申请的钛铁分离方法采用H2+Ar或H2+H2O+Ar的还原气氛，摆脱了采用煤基或碳基直接还原处理会增加污染物排放以及产生高钛渣的技术缺陷，具有低碳环保、还原温度低、无任何添加剂等优势，弱磁选后的磁选产物可为高炉或电炉提供生产原料，磁选尾矿可为制备钛铁合金提供方向，未来有望发展成为零排放清洁化矿物加工及冶炼的一种新概念工艺流程。"
                }
            ]
